rows.label: tlk70000051_04_msg0001
rows.name:
You came by just to say hi? You don't
need to worry about us, you know.

rows.label: tlk70000051_04_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm the leader of the Invidian contingent
here. I swear to uphold that title, even
when Adel isn't here.

rows.label: tlk70000051_04_msg0003
rows.name:
No matter who starts trying to stick
their oar in, king or no king, I'll be
here like "No! Piss off!"

rows.label: tlk70000051_04_msg0004
rows.name:
When you get back, we'll grab some
drinks and have a good old feast.

rows.label: tlk70000051_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Looking forward to hearing some of
your stories! Don't let me down, now.
